('CHE220', 'Computational Methods in Chemical Engineering I ', 'Introduces computational approaches and software applied to solve problems in chemical engineering. Software includes spreadsheet programs (Excel), high level computing languages (MATLAB), and chemical process simulation tools (Aspen, HYSYS).', 3.00, 'CHE', 0.00, 0),
