('CHE450', 'Chemical Process Industries ', 'Chemical engineering juniors and seniors. Combines process heuristics and design strategies with case studies of the industrial manufacture of a variety of materials, including petrochemicals, polymers, and ammonia. Discusses operational and design problems as well as the interactions of process principles.', 3.00, 'CHE', 0.00, 0),
